[quote=“I Vain I, post:1, topic:357181”]First picture: Try the client’s class9.

Second picture: Try the server’s textHandler.

Third picture: Try the client’s class9 (for the text) and the sprites (for the images)

Last picture, try the server’s clickingMost.[/quote]
